      • doGet

        public HttpRequest doGet(java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService executor,
                         HttpCallback callback)
        从类复制的说明: HttpRequest
        Perform http GET request. If executor param is null,will use default thread pool to submit the request. if callback param is null,call HttpRequest.getResponse() to get Response. Be careful that,if HttpResponseHandler is null,you should call HttpRequest.cancel() to reset all resource after response success of failed!
        覆盖:
        doGet 在类中 HttpRequest
        参数:
        executor - request thread pool or null.
        callback - Async request callback or null.
        返回:
        HttpRequest

Be careful that,if HttpResponseHandler is null,you should call HttpRequest.cancel() to reset all resource after response success of failed!
